r3827 | ncbray@google.com | Wed Dec 01 12:04:55 PST 2010

Changed paths:
 M http://src.chromium.org/viewvc/chrome/trunk/src/native_client/SConstruct?r1=3827&amp;r2=3826&amp;pathrev=3827

SCons makefile: fixed breakage of --verbose introduced by r3814

When verbose was specified, target_stats defaulted to on which disabled command printing.
This CL allows target_stats to function without interfering with command printing.

Code that printed the size of each binary was also removed because it would cause SCons to
relink binaries if --verbose changed between builds.

BUG=http://code.google.com/p/nativeclient/issues/detail?id=1207
TEST=./scons --verbose

